Maintainer: Patrick Schleizer <adrelanos@kicksecure.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 13), debhelper-compat (= 13)
Homepage: https://github.com/Kicksecure/user-admin-split
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/Kicksecure/user-admin-split
