Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: user-admin-split
Architecture: all
Depends: security-misc, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Role-Based Boot Modes - user versus admin
 Adds a GRUB boot menu entry "PERSISTENT mode ADMIN
 (For administrative tasks.)"
 .
 Makes Privilege Escalation Tools (such as sudo, su,
 pkexec) inaccessible to limited user accounts such as user "user".
 .
 Adds kernel parameter "boot-role=admin".
